{"tid":2031873,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"可靠消息：日落政府其實無視渴求民主自由的香港，甚至更偏向幫中共","createTime":"2020-05-23T16:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T18:50:31.000Z","uid":167177,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"88e1141e0ffc442b93040a3e3012a8584c5e6d67","tid":2031873,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"不過當地民間聲音好大，接近全力撐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以你地成日睇到日落政府同民間聲音不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息由來：英國資深政治學者<br />\n<br />\n我都係從佢口中打聽返黎，唔好問我詳情，我無深究。"},{"pid":"409e66fbf36d36fa1c010145ca8b7ebd9065e133","tid":2031873,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"哦，等下議院結果"},{"pid":"807f23f8cb6b6a54dc347ec5c90493d936943021","tid":2031873,"uid":20099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88e1141e0ffc442b93040a3e3012a8584c5e6d67","tid":2031873,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"不過當地民間聲音好大，接近全力撐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以你地成日睇到日落政府同民間聲音不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息由來：英國資深政治學者<br />\n<br />\n我都係從佢口中打聽返黎，唔好問我詳情，我無深究。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"有冇source"},{"pid":"89acdc4a2fb9fbe6947efa4615c0c96048dfbe0c","tid":2031873,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"我信，英國政府不嬲只睇利益不理公義，佢地國策不嬲都係有奶便是娘！"},{"pid":"77db520567beea38de02a5a9f1acaa060b73cbd2","tid":2031873,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"又放負<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=ee1f03f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"5d3fcc7547c2d03543d65e31a168f60a10303dc2","tid":2031873,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"三更半夜係時候幫人拉post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db811faf3a15cc2e7b1bdb5c6d5249321d2e2861","tid":2031873,"uid":49994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c5399e99b3dbe02394d282b36184eb8655c4dc","tid":2031873,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"我無放負，你地睇下美國踢在幾多次佢先肯放棄華惠就知。<br />\n我只不過係想大家信自己！"},{"pid":"b57d19ca3c29eb7b998e0a4c9afb07999b0d2e4d",